                                    This voucher rotates every 30 minutes for your protection. The current code is valid until {new Date(tokenExpiry || 0).toLocaleTimeString([], {hour: '2-digit', minute:'2-digit'})}.
                                </p>
                             </div>
                        </div>

                        {/* Primary Finish Button */}
                        <button 
